            "chapterTitle": "Excellence of Good Hopes",
            "urn": 1604370,
            "body": "<p>Jabir bin 'Abdullah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: I heard the Prophet (\ufdfa) saying three days before his death: \"Let none of you die unless he has good expectations from Allah\".<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
